title: 'Little Voice'
description:
If you like musical TV, check out 'Little Voice.' Created by Sara Bareilles and produced by JJ Abrams, it follows a struggling musician trying to make it in a fantastical New York City.

Hosts: Juliet Litman and Chris Ryan
